				\begin{document}$$C_{abs} = \Delta m/m_0,$$\end{document}where, Cabs is the moisture absorption capacity based on unit weight of raw NFM (g g−1), Δm is the moisture absorption quantity (g), and m0 is the weight of dried raw NFM (g).
